data.description: Do not miss this opportunity!  Welcome to this charming three bedroom, one bath single family home nestled in the heart of Manteca.  Perfect for first-time buyers or downsizing family.  This delightful property boast a newer kitchen with granite countertops, newer AC, dual pane windows, ceiling fans, one year exterior painting, alley access, corner lot and more.  This cute home is located near highway, shopping areas, and schools, It is a reflection of love and care! You will love this home, come and see it.
